      • performProximitySearch

        public IQueryBeanResult performProximitySearch(com.guidewire.pl.web.navigation.Location webLocation,
                                      ABContactSearchCriteria csc,
                                      ABContactSearchSpecWithoutPaging searchSpec,
                                      boolean isClearBundle)
        Performs a proximity search given using the provided ContactSearchCriteria. Will retrieve Geocodes for the ProximitySearchCenter, if necessary.
        Parameters:
        webLocation - the current Location
        csc - an ABContactSearchCriteria object
        searchSpec - Search spec to control various aspects of the search
        isClearBundle - - if true, then the bundle of the ABContactSearchCriteria will be cleared before performing the search so that only the criteria is left in the bundle. Should set this to true if calling from UI because Pebbles will not clear the bundle when user stays on the same page. (See jira CC-28078 for more details) *
        Returns:
        a QueryProcessor object
